timelineItems.desc: A vital meeting in the Western Conference is ahead when Seattle Sounders FC return home to take on Sporting Kansas City on Saturday evening at CenturyLink Field.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: Seattle Sounders vs Sporting Kansas City | May 23, 2015

timelineItems.name: Sam McDowell
timelineItems.text: That's a final. The top-two scoring teams in the Western Conference play to a scoreless draw in Seattle. Go figure. #SportingKC

timelineItems.desc: A vital meeting in the Western Conference is ahead when Seattle Sounders FC return home to take on Sporting Kansas City on Saturday evening at CenturyLink Field.
